Operating income for the two months ended December 31, 2014 was $6 million. As the contracts were designed to recover a majority of the costs incurred, operating income reflects only the recognition of the obligation,net of accretion, related to the below market contract, less a small amount of depreciation and amortization that is not included as part of the recoverable costs.
